<title>BULGARIA: Bulgaria to offer 3, 6-mth discount T-bills Monday.</title>
<headline>Bulgaria to offer 3, 6-mth discount T-bills Monday.</headline>
<dateline>SOFIA 1997-07-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bulgaria's Finance Ministry will offer on Monday two discount T-bill issues with a total value of 30 billion levs and with maturities of three and six months respectively, Finance Ministry figures showed.</p>
<p>The T-bills will be offered with no minimum acceptable prices set in advance, the ministry said.</p>
<p>Details of the offers follow:</p>
<p> Issue number	   BG3041497002	BG3041597009</p>
<p> Maturity		 three months	six months</p>
<p> Par value		10 bln levs	 20 bln levs</p>
<p> Auction date	   July 28	     July 28</p>
<p> Issue date	     July 30	     July 30</p>
<p> Maturity date	  October 29	  January 28, 1998</p>
<p>-- Sofia Newsroom, (++359-2) 91188</p>
